      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "collects rainwater drops"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "and deposit in the rooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 499260.0,
      "text": "But apart from this system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "they designed 52 beautiful water bodies around this town."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "And what we call private public partnership"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "you can add estate also."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "So, estate, public and private entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "work together to build this beautiful water body."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a kind of water body for all seasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "You will admire it. Just behold the beauty throughout the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "Whether water level goes up or down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 533260.0,
      "text": "the beauty is there throughout."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "Another water body, dried up, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "during the summer period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "but you can see how the traditional society"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "combines engineering with aesthetics, with the heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 551260.0,
      "text": "These statues, marvelous statues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "gives you an idea of water table."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "When this rain comes and the water starts filling this tank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "it will submerge these beautiful statues"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "in what we call in English today \"mass communication.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 568260.0,
      "text": "This was for mass communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 568260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "Everybody in the town will know that this elephant has drowned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 575260.0,
      "text": "so water will be there for seven months or nine months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 575260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "or 12 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "And then they will come and worship this pond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "pay respect, their gratitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 586260.0,
      "text": "Another small water body, called the [unclear]."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 588260.0,
      "text": "It is difficult to translate in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 588260.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "especially in my English."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "But the nearest would be \"glory,\" a reputation."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "The reputation in desert of this small water body is"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "that it never dries up."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "In severe drought periods"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "nobody has seen this water body"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 607260.0,
      "text": "getting dried up."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 607260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "And perhaps they knew the future also."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "It was designed some 150 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "But perhaps they knew that on sixth, November, 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "there will be a TED green and blue session,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "so they painted it like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 636260.0,
      "text": "Dry water body. Children are standing on"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 636260.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "a very difficult device to explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 639260.0,
      "end_time": 644260.0,
      "text": "This is called kund. We have, in English, surface water and ground water."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 644260.0,
      "end_time": 646260.0,
      "text": "But this is not ground water."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 646260.0,
      "end_time": 648260.0,
      "text": "You can draw ground water from any well."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 648260.0,
      "end_time": 651260.0,
      "text": "But this is no ordinary well."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 651260.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "It squeeze the moisture"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "hidden in the sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 661260.0,
      "text": "And they have dubbed this water as the third one called [unclear]."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 661260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "And there is a gypsum belt running below it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "And it was deposited by the great mother Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 673260.0,
      "text": "some three million years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 673260.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "And where we have this gypsum strip"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "they can harvest this water."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 680260.0,
      "text": "This is the same dry water body."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 680260.0,
      "end_time": 683260.0,
      "text": "Now, you don&#39;t find any kund;"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 683260.0,
      "end_time": 685260.0,
      "text": "they are all submerged."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 685260.0,
      "end_time": 688260.0,
      "text": "But when the water goes down they will be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 688260.0,
      "end_time": 691260.0,
      "text": "to draw water from those structures throughout the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 691260.0,
      "end_time": 695260.0,
      "text": "This year they have received only six centimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 695260.0,
      "end_time": 698260.0,
      "text": "Six centimeter of rainfall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 698260.0,
      "end_time": 700260.0,
      "text": "and they can telephone you"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 700260.0,
      "end_time": 703260.0,
      "text": "that if you find any water problem in your city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 703260.0,
      "end_time": 705260.0,
      "text": "Delhi, Bombay, Bangalore, Mysore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 705260.0,
      "end_time": 709260.0,
      "text": "please come to our area of six centimeters, we can give you water."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 709260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 712260.0,
      "text": "How they maintain them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 712260.0,
      "end_time": 715260.0,
      "text": "There are three things: concept, planning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 715260.0,
      "end_time": 718260.0,
      "text": "making the actual thing, and also maintaining them."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 718260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "It is a structure for maintain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 720260.0,
      "end_time": 725260.0,
      "text": "for centuries, by generations, without any department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 727260.0,
      "text": "without any funding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 727260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "So the secret is \"[unclear],\" respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "Your own thing, not personal property,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 736260.0,
      "end_time": 739260.0,
      "text": "my property, every time."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 741260.0,
      "text": "So, these stone pillars"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 741260.0,
      "end_time": 745260.0,
      "text": "will remind you that you are entering into a water body area."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 745260.0,
      "end_time": 747260.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t spit, don&#39;t do anything wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 747260.0,
      "end_time": 750260.0,
      "text": "so that the clean water can be collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 750260.0,
      "end_time": 753260.0,
      "text": "Another pillar, stone pillar on your right side."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 753260.0,
      "end_time": 756260.0,
      "text": "If you climb these three, six steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 756260.0,
      "end_time": 759260.0,
      "text": "you will find something very nice."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 759260.0,
      "end_time": 762260.0,
      "text": "This was done in 11th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 762260.0,
      "end_time": 765260.0,
      "text": "And you have to go further down."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 765260.0,
      "end_time": 768260.0,
      "text": "They say that a picture is worth a thousand words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 768260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "so we can say a thousand words right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 771260.0,
      "end_time": 773260.0,
      "text": "an another thousand words."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 773260.0,
      "end_time": 775260.0,
      "text": "If the water table goes down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 775260.0,
      "end_time": 777260.0,
      "text": "you will find new stairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 777260.0,
      "end_time": 781260.0,
      "text": "If it comes up, some of them will be submerged."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 781260.0,
      "end_time": 783260.0,
      "text": "So, throughout the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 788260.0,
      "text": "this beautiful system will give you some pleasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 788260.0,
      "end_time": 790260.0,
      "text": "Three sides, such steps, on the fourth side"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 790260.0,
      "end_time": 792260.0,
      "text": "there is a four-story building"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 792260.0,
      "end_time": 797260.0,
      "text": "where you can organize such TED conferences anytime."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 797260.0,
      "end_time": 803260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 803260.0,
      "end_time": 807260.0,
      "text": "Excuse me, who built these structures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 807260.0,
      "end_time": 809260.0,
      "text": "They are in front of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 809260.0,
      "end_time": 813260.0,
      "text": "The best civil engineers we had, the best planners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 813260.0,
      "end_time": 815260.0,
      "text": "the best architects."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 815260.0,
      "end_time": 817260.0,
      "text": "We can say that because of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 817260.0,
      "end_time": 819260.0,
      "text": "because of their forefathers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 819260.0,
      "end_time": 822260.0,
      "text": "India could get the first engineering college"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 822260.0,
      "end_time": 825260.0,
      "text": "in 1847."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 825260.0,
      "end_time": 828260.0,
      "text": "There were no English medium schools at that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 828260.0,
      "end_time": 831260.0,
      "text": "even no Hindi schools, [unclear] schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 831260.0,
      "end_time": 834260.0,
      "text": "But such people, compelled to the East India Company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 834260.0,
      "end_time": 838260.0,
      "text": "which came here for business, a very dirty kind of business ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 838260.0,
      "end_time": 840260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 840260.0,
      "end_time": 843260.0,
      "text": "but not to create the engineering colleges."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 843260.0,
      "end_time": 847260.0,
      "text": "But because of them, first engineering college was created"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 847260.0,
      "end_time": 850260.0,
      "text": "in a small village, not in the town."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 850260.0,
      "end_time": 855260.0,
      "text": "The last point, we all know in our primary schools that"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 855260.0,
      "end_time": 858260.0,
      "text": "that camel is a ship of desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 858260.0,
      "end_time": 861260.0,
      "text": "So, you can find through your Jeep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 861260.0,
      "end_time": 864260.0,
      "text": "a camel, and a cart."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 864260.0,
      "end_time": 868260.0,
      "text": "This tire comes from the airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 868260.0,
      "end_time": 871260.0,
      "text": "So, look at the beauty from the desert society"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 871260.0,
      "end_time": 873260.0,
      "text": "who can harvest rainwater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 873260.0,
      "end_time": 876260.0,
      "text": "and also create something"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 876260.0,
      "end_time": 880260.0,
      "text": "through a tire from a jet plane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 880260.0,
      "end_time": 882260.0,
      "text": "and used in a camel cart."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 882260.0,
      "end_time": 885260.0,
      "text": "Last picture, it&#39;s a tattoo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 885260.0,
      "end_time": 887260.0,
      "text": "2,000-years-old tattoo."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 887260.0,
      "end_time": 890260.0,
      "text": "They were using it on their body."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 890260.0,
      "end_time": 892260.0,
      "text": "Tattoo was, at one time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 892260.0,
      "end_time": 894260.0,
      "text": "a kind of a blacklisted"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 894260.0,
      "end_time": 897260.0,
      "text": "or con thing, but now it is in thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 897260.0,
      "end_time": 899260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 899260.0,
      "end_time": 901260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 901260.0,
      "end_time": 904260.0,
      "text": "You can copy this tattoo. I have some posters of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 904260.0,
      "end_time": 907260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 907260.0,
      "end_time": 912260.0,
      "text": "The center of life is water."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 912260.0,
      "end_time": 914260.0,
      "text": "These are the beautiful waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 914260.0,
      "end_time": 917260.0,
      "text": "These are the beautiful stairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 917260.0,
      "end_time": 920260.0,
      "text": "which we just saw in one of the slides."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 920260.0,
      "end_time": 923260.0,
      "text": "These are the trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 923260.0,
      "end_time": 925260.0,
      "text": "And these are the flowers which"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 925260.0,
      "end_time": 929260.0,
      "text": "add fragrance to our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 929260.0,
      "end_time": 932260.0,
      "text": "So, this is the message of desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 932260.0,
      "end_time": 934260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 934260.0,
      "end_time": 960260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 960260.0,
      "end_time": 964260.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: So, first of all, I wish I had your eloquence, truly, in any language."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 964260.0,
      "end_time": 971260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 971260.0,
      "end_time": 977260.0,
      "text": "These artifacts and designs are inspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 977260.0,
      "end_time": 980260.0,
      "text": "Do you believe that they can be used elsewhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 980260.0,
      "end_time": 982260.0,
      "text": "that the world can learn from this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 982260.0,
      "end_time": 984260.0,
      "text": "Or is this just right for this place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 984260.0,
      "end_time": 987260.0,
      "text": "Anupam Mishra: No, the basic idea is to"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 987260.0,
      "end_time": 990260.0,
      "text": "utilize water that falls on our area."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 990260.0,
      "end_time": 994260.0,
      "text": "So, the ponds, the open bodies, are everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 994260.0,
      "end_time": 999260.0,
      "text": "right from Sri Lanka to Kashmir, and in other parts also."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 999260.0,
      "end_time": 1002260.0,
      "text": "And these [unclear], which stored water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1002260.0,
      "end_time": 1004260.0,
      "text": "there are two type of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1004260.0,
      "end_time": 1006260.0,
      "text": "One recharge, and one stores."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1006260.0,
      "end_time": 1009260.0,
      "text": "So, it depends on the terrain."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1009260.0,
      "end_time": 1012260.0,
      "text": "But kund, which uses the gypsum belt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1012260.0,
      "end_time": 1016260.0,
      "text": "for that you have to go back to your calendar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1016260.0,
      "end_time": 1018260.0,
      "text": "three million years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1018260.0,
      "end_time": 1020260.0,
      "text": "If it is there it can be done right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1020260.0,
      "end_time": 1022260.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, it can&#39;t be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1022260.0,
      "end_time": 1023260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1023260.0,
      "end_time": 1025260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1025260.0,
      "end_time": 1027260.0,
      "text": "CA: Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1027260.0,
      "end_time": 1029260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}